<ul class="project-title-and-text">

    <li class="project-title">
        Charisma House Website Redesign
    </li>

    <li class="project-type">
        Web Design
    </li>

    <li class="project-tools">
        Webflow, HTML, CSS, JavaScript
    </li>

    <li class="project-objective-title">
        About
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text">
        Charisma House is a Japanese music multimedia project by King Records. This is a full redesign of their web
        presence, built in Webflow with custom JavaScript for interactions Webflow doesn't natively support.
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text-2">
        The design started with low-fidelity Figma wireframes across desktop, tablet, and mobile before moving into
        Webflow. Bold colors and eye-catching typography were chosen to match the project's flamboyant, spontaneous
        energy — staying faithful to the existing brand while giving it a completely new visual register.
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text-2">
        The site includes a landing page, individual character profiles with introductory voice lines, a news page,
        episode releases, a merch store link, and a live Twitter feed.
    </li>

    <li class="oreo-guidelines-button">
        <a class="resume-button-text" href="https://web-3-pm-demo-6c4b5c.webflow.io/final-project" target="_blank">
            View the live site!
        </a>
    </li>
</ul>

